WEBVTT

00:00.696 --> 00:02.562
<i>Previously on "Manhattan"...</i>

00:05.851 --> 00:07.952
<i>When the time comes,
someone will contact you.</i>

00:07.986 --> 00:11.322
He'll have the other half
of this.

00:11.324 --> 00:12.823
- Crosley.
- Hi.

00:12.825 --> 00:14.825
This is really
not a good time.

00:14.876 --> 00:17.128
Are you...

00:17.162 --> 00:18.713
We'll be forming
a new test group.

00:18.747 --> 00:20.715
<i>There will be
an announcement soon.</i>

00:20.749 --> 00:22.833
How did you know that
Mrs. Winter was the girl for you?

00:22.835 --> 00:25.386
<i>Was it like Einstein discovering
spatial relativity?</i>

00:25.420 --> 00:27.004
That took Albert
a couple years.

00:27.055 --> 00:29.140
- I'm Abby.
- Elodie.

00:29.174 --> 00:31.392
<i>Enchant√©.</i>

00:31.926 --> 00:34.228
- Callie!
<i>-  Sorry, ma'am.</i>

00:34.262 --> 00:36.263
<i>If you took her away,
I'd never see her again.</i>

00:38.350 --> 00:40.017
<i>There was an
incident in Ithaca.</i>

00:40.068 --> 00:41.519
<i>I made a mistake.</i>

00:41.521 --> 00:44.071
You're all right now,
aren't you?

00:44.106 --> 00:46.657
Jesus, Glen, I can't
do this without you.

00:46.691 --> 00:50.361
You're gonna have to.
They want me off the Hill.

00:50.363 --> 00:53.364
- Where is he?
-<i> Your husband is at another site</i>

00:53.415 --> 00:55.366
proving his loyalty
to his country.

